
to run the scripts do the following:

mkdir <dir>
git clone https://github.com/iflanagan/SauceConnectHAScripts.git
cd <dir>
NOTE: sauce connect proxy versions may change check here for the latest one
https://wiki.saucelabs.com/display/DOCS/Downloading+Sauce+Connect+Proxy

wget https://saucelabs.com/downloads/sc-4.5.4-osx.zip
tar -xvf tar -xvf sc-4.5.4-osx.zip
mv sc-4.5.4-osx SauceConnect

edit SCScriptOne and SCScriptTwo file paths
chmod 755 SCScriptOne
chmod 755 SCScriptTwo 

./SCScriptOne <tunnelIdentifier>
./SCScriptTwo <tunnelIdentifier>

NOTE: Be sure to use the same <tunnelIdentifier> when calling both scripts

now set a crontab and call 

checkScript


